snippet.title: Peaked Interest
snippet.description:
Hi, this is Peaked Interest, the youtube channel where I do deep dives about things that I find interesting. Sometimes its true stories and crime, sometimes it's movies, sometimes it's just things I find amusing. 

and yes...I know the common use is piqued interest but I chose peaked on purpose to represent when your interest reaches it's peak.. because that's what I do here :-)

Thanks for watching
